description: Application for Non-Material amendment to reserved matters approval for Phase 1 under ref: PA/22/00905, Dated 14/12/2022.Non-Material amendment(s) sought: Amendments to the private housing mix, including redistribution of units and creation of an additional private unit,Internal layout changes,Minor floorspace changes including reduction in residential GIA floorspace and increase in commercial GIA floorspace,Minor elevational amendments including window height changes, ground floor louvre rationalisation, introduction of louvres on the upper levels, and changes to the location of balconies,Reduction in the size of the roof plant, andInclusion of transfer structure above the ground floor along the west and north-west elevations.
site_name: Bow Common Gas Works, Bow Common Lane, London
